{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":{"eng-name":"The Chapters on Marriage","ara-name":"كتاب النكاح"}},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1890,"arabicnumber":1890,"text":"। আবূ সাঈদ আল-খুদরী (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম ‘আয়িশাহ্ (রাঃ) -কে একটি ঘরের আসবাবপত্রের বিনিময়ে বিবাহ করেন, যার মূল্য ছিল পঞ্চাশ দিরহাম।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":46},"chapter":{"id":17,"ara-name":"باب صَدَاقِ النِّسَاءِ","eng-name":"Dowries of women","isFirstHadith":false}}]}